value.title: Donald Trump Target Of Ricin Poisoned Letter For Second Time
value.excerpt: A letter containing the poison Ricin was intercepted before arrival on President Donald Trump’s desk for the second time, according to law enforcement officials. value.title: Fox News' Brit Hume begs Trump to not push through Ginsberg replacement before the election
